Class WhereToken.LongWhereDetails

  • java.lang.Object

  • Enclosing class:
    WhereToken

    public class WhereToken.LongWhereDetails
extends WhereToken.AbstractWhereDetails<java.lang.Long,NumberCondition>
    A simple data container, specifying the details of a WhereToken in the query language.

    This version is specialized for "where" clauses that act on Long values.
